code: @Override protected Set<ConfigurableApplicationContext> findApplicationContexts() {     Set<ConfigurableApplicationContext> contexts = new LinkedHashSet<>().     Enumeration<String> attrNames = this.servletContext.getAttributeNames().     while (attrNames.hasMoreElements()) {         String attrName = attrNames.nextElement().         Object attrValue = this.servletContext.getAttribute(attrName).         if (attrValue instanceof ConfigurableApplicationContext) {             contexts.add((ConfigurableApplicationContext) attrValue).         }     }     return contexts. }
